[[!meta title="Sound and video"]]

Tails includes several sound and video applications:

  - [Audacity](http://audacity.sourceforge.net/) is a multi-track audio editor
    designed for recording, playing and editing of digital audio.
  - [Brasero](http://projects.gnome.org/brasero/) is an application to burn,
    copy, and erase CD and DVD media: audio, video or data.
  - [Pitivi](http://www.pitivi.org/)
  - [SoundJuicer](http://burtonini.com/blog/computers/sound-juicer) is a CD
    ripper application.
  - [Traverso](http://traverso-daw.org/) is a multi-track audio recorder and
    editor.

